Package civitas.celestis.math.vector

Interface LongVector<V extends LongVector<V,D>,D extends DoubleVector<D>>

Type Parameters:
V - Itself (the parameter and result of various operations)
D - The double vector corresponding to this vector's size
All Superinterfaces:
Group<Long>, Serializable, Vector<Long,V>
All Known Implementing Classes:
Long2, Long3, Long4
public interface LongVector<V extends LongVector<V,D>,D extends DoubleVector<D>> extends Vector<Long,V>
A vector which uses the type float.
